{"title":"翻身曲","authors":["史德"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":3,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻身曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唐山工人  史德"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起从前真心酸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不由人不泪涟涟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反动派，真混蛋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿人当做狗来看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是没有共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁来帮我们把身翻！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我现在作工有了工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你现在种地有了田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我作工、你种田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们大家搞生产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我举铁锤多加力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你使锄头耍的欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕累，不畏难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家齐心努力干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支援前线，消灭反动派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真正和平才能实现。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三·十五·"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}